node.Title: Protfolio Website
node.Description: This website itself, used as a protfolio extension to personal CV.

node.Title: Expendibots by Boomers
node.Description: Major project of Artificial Intelligence (COMP30024), which purpose is to strategically create an AI agent that plays the custom board game Expendibots.

node.Title: Prediction of COVID-19 in Vietnam
node.Description: An analysis and prediction of the COVID-19 statistics in Vietnam, using a variety of Machine Learning and mathematical methods. Served as a model for the COVID-19 prevention operation by Vietnam Ministry of Health.

node.Title: The Live Status of Novel Coronavirus in Australia
node.Description: Real time statistics website of the COVID-19 situation in Australia, founded by students of Monash University.

node.Title: CvTracker
node.Description: A website that conatins a collection of safety measurement detections at public areas during COVID-19 pandemic. Served as a hackathon project in Vietnam.
node.Contributor: Andrew Ngo, Nam Hoang, Ha Vu

node.Title: Server Learning Guide
node.Description: A learning journal during internship at Momo that can be used as a guide for elements of introductory server learning, such as ssh conncection or Linux commands.

node.Title: ShadowBounce Extension
node.Description: An extension of OOSD (SWEN20003) major game project, consisting of new elements, built-in cheat codes, hidden levels and a custom level generator.

node.Title: Pacman Agent Upgraded
node.Description: An upgraded version of ADS (COMP20003) AI Agent that plays the game of Pacman, which was applied with simple strategies and algorithms.
